Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of a sudden,\Nyou took my hand in yours{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that we wouldn't\Nget separated in the crowd{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so happy I couldn't squeeze\Nyour hand very tightly in return{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, I realized I was in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We started out as just friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now let's cross that boundary line{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And take off together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hold my feelings back\Nanymore It hurts so much I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, I can't lie to myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is embarrassing to ask, but{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please accept everything about me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, now and forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"The Greatest Bloodbath in History" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, stop sitting at that desk all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about getting outside a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to start getting\Nready for the next summer Comipa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flabbiness, puffiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize that your face has been\Nturning into a stereotypical otaku's lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be summer soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's why\NI'm getting ready for Comipa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comipa, Comipa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you've\Nresolved yourself, Comrade Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next year's World Cup in Germany,\Nand next month's summer Comipa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these two great\Nworldwide events ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--we sacrifice the brief\Nmoments of sun in the rainy season,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you going to do for the cover?\N--in order to press forward into a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's going to be in color with leafing on it!\N--secret training camp in an unexplored region.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't wait!\N--This shall be our first stept
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow...\N--towards world conquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to be going to a totally\Nnormal, ordinary, run-of-the-mill camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so how'd it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Major League Ball 3 was born
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through secret special training\Nheld out of the sight of the public,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through this training camp, we shall\Ntake the world in the palm of our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mountain Campground"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seriously saying\Nyou forgot the food, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am floored by your level\Nof misunderstanding, my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the amount of\Nbaggage becomes bulky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the occurrence of a slight\Nmiscalculation in loading strategies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is an inevitable result of current statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slight miscalculation?\NInevitable result of statistics?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure brought a lot of different stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a toy for\Nplaying in a hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anticipating various situations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is common practice\Nat a secret training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're telling me that\Nyou've forgotten our food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that the speed of light
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is 7 1/2 times the circumference\Nof the Earth, my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really don't have anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nada, zilch, absolutely nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, if we don't turn around and\Ngo back, we won't have anything to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there weren't any\Nstores at all on the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ticket, bus ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I poured my entire soul\Ninto selecting this final frontier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would easily take three hours\Nto reach the closest store by car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, it closes at 6:00 like\Nsome relic from the previous century.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the hot spring panda is rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you mean "dejected".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh nothing, this\Nroad just seems familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taishi! Did you just say we're lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hearing, my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said was, we took\Nonly one road to get here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before I realized it, we started\Ntraveling through unfamiliar territory
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which isn't recorded in my memory,\Nand I feel a certain ambivalence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if we keep going this way,\Nwon't we end up who knows where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know, just look ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this the same\Ncampground we just came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen?\NWe didn't go back down at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the legend is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a booby trap once set up by\Ndefeated warriors of the Heike clan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that they could\Nescape the pursuit of the Genji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once someone sets foot here,\Nthey must wander for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This campground is in an\Ninescapable forest of wandering,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is even compared to the\Ndense forest at the base of Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Forest of Wandering"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dense forest at...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The base of Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inescapable labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a three year old kid wouldn't\Nbelieve somethin' like that these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Out of Area"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think a cell phone\Nwould connect in a dense forest like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so patronizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sputnik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just great! The GPS is shot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?\NTry going back down again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we move through\Nthe dense forest carelessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a danger we\Ncould get even more lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki, a local old guy\Ncame asking what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A local old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there's actually\Nsomeone around a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the ones who are lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, actually, we got lost and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want us to tell you the route from\Nmy troop's garrison, back to the local town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I cannot relinquish\NClass 1 classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We understand, our destined rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must obtain the information\Nwe want through strategic maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the iron-clad rule ("okite") which\Ngoverns campgrounds all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, what does he mean\N"Soji Okita of the Campground?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taishi probably just made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way,\Nit's not Okita, it's okite (rule).
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to declare war on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't run away, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess this means we're going to\Nhave to play a survival game after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, Comrade Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a simple survival game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a sacred battle with\Nthe rule of the world at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sacred battle? With these laser gun toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\Nyou see this practice system,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is officially used by armies all\Nover the world, and has improved sim fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a mere children's plaything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It detects a beam with\Nan optical receiving device,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and acknowledges a good shot with\Nthe warning device worn on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the latest\Nsuper-interactive virtual device.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of it as a mere plaything, you\Nwill be the first to fall to an enemy bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Taishi, we're up\Nagainst survival game pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we even have any hope of winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade Kazuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thoughts deeper than the Mariana\NTrench run through my gray matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughts deeper than...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mariana Trench?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to teach you real\Ngood what the fear of death is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comic Party Revolution{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comic Party Revolution!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelbe Eins to Hertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't detect Fritz in Area 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hertz. Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed to Area 89 immediately,\Nand continue scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelbe Eins, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,victory or defeat depends entirely\Nupon how quickly you can find the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've polished our scouting\Nskills through numerous actual battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against us, you're just sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you probably do have good skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However! That will not\Nbe enough to win against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware that against our secret plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your skills are nothing\Nmore than a rusted door knocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be saying that when\Nyou just got shot in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Corpse"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Taishi Team Corpse Storage Site"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found them. Ahead\N100 meters. Two enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Attack them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelbe Eins, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you think you're hidden, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stupid amateurs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Corpse"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Team Corpse Storage Site"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the ultimate defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which utilizes the enemy's psychology\Nunder the extreme conditions of battle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to neutralize every\Nconceivable attack instantly:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Cosplay Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Cosplay Barrier"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems to be so\Neffective, I'm almost embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you witness our secret plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "secret plan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Co-Comrade Kazuki! It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It couldn't be," my ass. I was shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so pathetic when\Neveryone else is risking their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if we could defend ourselves,\Nwe can't go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Forget your\Nfragile-handle-with-cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am already waiting for\NSecret Plan 2 to be put into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Plan 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rebuild front line defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelbe Drei, proceed to Area 86...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be able to stop\NChisa Tsukamoto's headlong charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is even compared to the out-of-control\Nhuman dumptruck, Stan Hansen's rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All men, concentrate your\Nfire on the out of control cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what incredible speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can probably break\Nthrough the enemy's front line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a tinge of worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what nice tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Checkerboard Pattern"\NMy, what nice tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's boring being a corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the first one\Nshot, so it serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong about that, Comrade Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got shot in order to lure the\Nenemy into letting their guard down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an ingenious plan worthy of Hakuoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I despise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch you and\Ntoss you into a scorpion tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! And that! And that! And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay Barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly a terrifying strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is one\Nbig thing you overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cosplay Barrier didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys probably don't know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our captain has absolutely\Nno interest in girls aged over 1[censored].
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To our captain, girls who are\Nmore developed than necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the same as vegetables in a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they are nothing more than\Ndespicable, abominable creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so captivated by the floatation ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got dangerously close\Nto getting too excited, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your overly-developed\Nbody turned out to be your fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed that Fritz 7 is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. There's only one left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll switch to\Nsurround-and-destroy maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All men, converge on Area 85.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they think they've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However! You do not know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how frightening we truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the last one of us\Nleft is our ultimate weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be... A stealth human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does she have an\Noverwhelmingly weak presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she went virtually unnoticed\Neven in the Comipa Exhibition Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she continues to have a menacingly\Nhigh rate of doujinshi left unsold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the invisible\None-person circle, Aya Hasabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All men gather up and form a circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they possibly find Aya Hasabe\Nin this complex survival game field?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Where is she?\NWhere did she shoot from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost? Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the most perfect and beautiful victory in\Nthe history of mankind was accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great first step in our ambitions for\Nworld conquest has taken place right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you acting all high and mighty\Nfor when you're the one who got shot first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this is the first time my\Ntroop has been so completely defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such little\Npresence you're almost not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck,\Nthat's not a compliment at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Aya, I think\Nyou should get angry, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we won, so keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make a promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you would tell us\Nthe way to get back to town!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru is starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Right, we were supposed\Nto guide you from our garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been wandering\Nthis dense forest for a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we haven't sighted a\Nroute back down from the garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that means we're lost too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should have\Nsaid that in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me! You're my savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't been so kind as to stop me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisa would have ended\Nup becoming another Vostok,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going around and\Naround the Earth forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a town right on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been kinda worried about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't it seem like\Nwe're missin' somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's me you're thinking about,\NI'm right here, Comrade Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start living together right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's missing is time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think we need a place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where we can share our smiles,\Nour tears{\i0}, {\i1}and our free time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was with you,\NI could stay there forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you don't\Nlike anything complicated{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still keep on pulling your arms{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally found this 2LDK{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A table set would be fine too{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I think a kotatsu\Nwould be better after all{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time we spend\Njust lying around together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is more important than it sounds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not easy to find someone\Nyou can always accept{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And who will always accept you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you are that person for me, so{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start living together right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's missing is time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think we need a place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where we can share smiles,\Nour tears, and our free time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was with you,\NI could stay there forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm super pissed off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How dare you treat me, the Comipa Queen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Great Eimi Ohba,\Nlike some ordinary citizen?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh, um, Ms. Ohba?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you saying that I, the Great Eimi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}am not good enough to\Nbe Asahi Sakurai's friend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that's not it at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come down to this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just have to show you\Nthe Great Eimi's true powder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's "true power."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time: "Let's Start by Being Friends."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who's\Nalways standing in line...{\i0}
